description: Nestled in an upscale Southie community, this sunfilled residence boasts rare two-car garage parking, blending sophistication with unparalleled convenience. Enjoy the serenity of shared green spaces and proximity to scenic beaches and historic Castle Island. Within, find two spacious bedrooms and a versatile additional room, perfect for work or relaxation. The gourmet kitchen features European-inspired cabinetry, top-tier Bosch appliances, and striking Calacatta Gold quartz countertops, anchored by a spacious island. The master suite offers luxury with a marble en-suite, dual vanity, and radiant heated floors for ultimate comfort. Unique to this home are upgraded closets, a private entrance, and a deck off the den, enhancing its appeal. This haven is a testament to refined living, promising a lifestyle of elegance and convenience close to the heart of Southie's vibrant dining, leisure scene and Pet Friendly!
